Package: yzy
Title: Converting Measurements and Z-scores with Conditional References
Version: 0.5.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Stef",
           family = "van Buuren",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "stef.vanbuuren@tno.nl",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1098-2119"))
Description: Lightweight tool for conversion between measurements (y) and
    Z-scores (z) under conditional reference distributions. Defines a simple 
    text format for exchanging reference distributions. Provides tools to read, 
    validate, name and load references as R objects. Supported distributions: 
    Normal, LMS, Box-Cox Green Cole (BCCG), Box-Cox Power Exponential (BCPE) 
    and Box-Cox t (BCT).
License: AGPL (>= 3) + file LICENSE
